sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as Web Client
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant UseCase as Bank Account Creation Use Case
    participant BSTHandler as Bank Statement Handler
    participant S3 as AWS S3
    participant EventBus as Event Bus
    participant OCR as OCR / AI Service
    participant Ledger as Ledger Repository

    User->>App: Submits Name & Currency
    
    alt Option 1: Manual Opening Balance
        App->>API: POST /api/ledgers/bank-accounts (Balance)
        API->>UseCase: CreateAccountCmd
        UseCase->>Ledger: Create Sub-Ledger (101xxx)
        UseCase->>Ledger: Create Suspense Ledger (100100)
        UseCase->>Ledger: Create OBE Sub-Ledger (300xxx)
        Note over UseCase,Ledger: System offsets Opening Balance<br/>against Opening Balance Equity (Sub-Ledger)
        UseCase->>Ledger: Post Opening Balance Journal
        UseCase-->>API: 201 Created
        API-->>User: Success
        
    else Option 2: Statement Upload
        App->>API: POST /api/ledgers/bank-accounts (with PDF)
        API->>UseCase: CreateAccountWithStatementCmd
        UseCase->>Ledger: Create Sub-Ledger (101xxx)
        UseCase->>Ledger: Create Suspense Ledger (100100)
        UseCase->>Ledger: Create OBE Sub-Ledger (300xxx)
        UseCase->>S3: Upload Statement PDF
        UseCase->>EventBus: Publish StatementUploadedEvent
        UseCase-->>API: 204 No Content
        API-->>User: UI: "Working in background..."
        
        %% Async Processing Flow
        EventBus->>OCR: Consume StatementUploadedEvent
        activate OCR
        OCR->>OCR: Extract Transactions & Opening Bal
        OCR->>OCR: AI Auto-Categorization & Transfer Prediction
        OCR->>EventBus: Publish TransactionsExtractedEvent
        deactivate OCR

        EventBus->>BSTHandler: Consume TransactionsExtractedEvent
        Note over BSTHandler,Ledger: System offsets Opening Balance<br/>against Opening Balance Equity (Sub-Ledger)
        BSTHandler->>Ledger: Post Opening Balance Journal
        BSTHandler->>Ledger: Store Raw Transactions in Suspense Ledger (100100)
        BSTHandler->>App: Push Notification: "Ready for Review"
        
        %% User Review Flow
        App-->>User: Prompt to Review Categories/Transfers
        User->>App: Review & Modify Descriptions (Amt/Date Locked)
        App->>API: POST /api/reconciliation/match
        API->>UseCase: ReconcileTransactionsCmd
        UseCase->>Ledger: Clear Suspense (100100) & Credit Target Accounts
        UseCase-->>User: Reconciled & Recorded
    end